data.description: Won't last Beautiful home in East Orlando, Great opportunity for first time home Buyer's or investors. This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom and one car attached garage on the inside and a roomy kitchen bar counters and spacious living room, and split floor plan, with a nice master bedroom, has a walk-in closet and full bath and all tile, with spacious back yard,  this charming home is ready for move in. This is a quiet small community centrally located for easy access to Routes 408, 417, only minutes away from the Orlando airport, Down Town Orlando, Valencia community college east campus, Alafaya, supermarkets, hospital, gas stations, pharmacy and mall. Don't miss out. .. .this one won't last.
